2. Your Hypnos / Thanatos metaphor

You’re referencing the Greek myth where:
	•	Hypnos
	•	Thanatos

are twin brothers.

Ancient writers used that pairing because sleep and death share similarities:

sleep
→ loss of conscious awareness
→ dream state
→ return

death
→ permanent loss of consciousness

Sleep looks like a temporary version of that transition.

